{"id": 2918, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都经历/发现了哪些当代生活悖论？", "description": "啊，谜一样的，当代生活。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Bellott）", "record_count": 4066, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190425180820moS4gzbHQcLahEJ2.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-05T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 342784, "content": "加班是为了项目时间变短，但是由于加班，导致第二天的工作效率降低，最后发现可能工作时间变长反而导致项目时间变长", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633295}, {"id": 342786, "content": "共享充电宝，手机没电了借不了咋充电", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609848}, {"id": 342788, "content": "买房导致生活质量严重下降，其实只是前三年的适应调整期，之后就好达成新的生活平衡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644468}, {"id": 342789, "content": "做着喜欢事情怀疑自己是不是喜欢的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547881}, {"id": 342794, "content": "越长大越孤单，越孤单越不想长大！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649250}, {"id": 343062, "content": "奥卡姆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1562951}, {"id": 342809, "content": "想让婆婆帮忙，但又各种嫌弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 342813, "content": "年轻时候有大把时间身体又好可没钱去做想做的事，年纪大了有钱了又做不了了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549408}, {"id": 343339, "content": "明明明天吃很多睡很多，却还是很累，没有力气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415925}, {"id": 342828, "content": "为了省钱上淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644123}, {"id": 344367, "content": "自己做不到的事情 却要求他人做到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498264}, {"id": 342837, "content": "渴望别人主动来找自己聊天，但又不想聊太久.", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648406}, {"id": 342865, "content": "鼓励与优秀的人交朋友，不结交比你差的人-----------如果优秀的人也是这样想的呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649414}, {"id": 342879, "content": "吐槽老板和同事的朋友圈，必须屏蔽老板和同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333758}, {"id": 342626, "content": "单身的时候想要恋爱，恋爱的时候想要分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619616}, {"id": 342627, "content": "嘴上说着一个人挺好不想谈恋爱，看到别人成双入队秀恩爱就开始既柠檬精又渴望爱情，终究是自己不懂得如何爱与被爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 440, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428095}, {"id": 342884, "content": "本栏目中好奇心提供优秀回答是为了抛砖引玉，然而大家都觉得写得好，就不自己写了，所以好奇心需要写的更多……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087927}, {"id": 342630, "content": "小时候读得励志故事里面，主人公都是勤工俭学努力工作只为读书，长大发现，读书都是为了能有一份工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 165, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141821}, {"id": 342631, "content": "不想谈恋爱是因为没遇到喜欢的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615602}, {"id": 342632, "content": "相约出去玩，却各自玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 185, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618426}, {"id": 343144, "content": "不想一个人待着，但是又不想跟别人聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635276}, {"id": 342633, "content": "骗子太多…最后连受害者自身咋瞅着鬼头鬼脑的像骗子。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593677}, {"id": 342635, "content": "想努力工作为家人带来更好的生活，但没有时间陪伴家人，家人的生活并不是那么好", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 346219, "content": "我想努力，可是想要的奖励凭自己的努力却无法得到，被打垮。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}, {"id": 342636, "content": "看到别人在朋友圈炫耀不屑点赞；自己也在朋友圈炫耀却希望别人来点赞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213460}, {"id": 342638, "content": "不将就", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621286}, {"id": 342639, "content": "不将就，最大的悖论", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621286}, {"id": 342640, "content": "所有要做的事情都会赶在同一时间段突然爆炸出现。而且，越是在最忙的时候，越会突然有私活找上门。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146608}, {"id": 342641, "content": "看谁都不像好人😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456423}, {"id": 342642, "content": "要有经验才能做这份工作，但不得到这份工作就没有经验啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 429, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151248}, {"id": 342644, "content": "看朋友圈里各种美景美食无比羡慕，真出去玩的时候心里却只想赶快回家里躺尸", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335539}, {"id": 342645, "content": "努力不一定有收获，越努力不一定越幸运。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559203}, {"id": 342647, "content": "微信里一千个好友，生活中一个都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835026}, {"id": 342648, "content": "我又懒又想要数不清的财富但没有一个富豪爹\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316115}, {"id": 342650, "content": "自己矫情/嫌弃别人矫情", "image": "img/option/option/20190505123402Mo6blrk0Gnqwu1VO.jpg", "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266913}, {"id": 342651, "content": "底层人民拥有平凡的幸福", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596345}, {"id": 342652, "content": "避开高峰出游，不是高峰也没假出游啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646975}, {"id": 342653, "content": "你觉得自己在做自己 但其实不是", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596097}, {"id": 342654, "content": "人们渴望过得别人不一样 \n但是又害怕不一样的眼光\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647470}, {"id": 342655, "content": "我不能玩吃鸡了，cheing", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329164}, {"id": 342656, "content": "我看着天真的我自己，出现在没有我的世界里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555580}, {"id": 342657, "content": "看起来人人都在吐槽网红店，但排队排最长的也是它们", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333758}, {"id": 342658, "content": "想交朋友却有不想去交", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202602}, {"id": 342659, "content": "一边对别人的炫耀表示鄙夷，一边想炫耀又怕被嘲笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464789}, {"id": 342664, "content": "想做爱好相关的工作，并从中赚钱；以赚钱为目的后发现，这个爱好不再是爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648888}, {"id": 342921, "content": "看手机上写手机危害的报道，看的不亦乐乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614210}, {"id": 342666, "content": "怕犯错误，有了这个想法后更容易犯错误，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509413}, {"id": 342667, "content": "觉得自己条件挺好的。人长得不差、善良大方得体可爱积极乐观，却一直单身着……", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648894}, {"id": 342668, "content": "22岁了，不知道自己想要啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626629}, {"id": 342669, "content": "不讲究，不将就。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369175}]}